<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Privacy Policy — <%= businessName %></title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/img/favicon.ico" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("partials/header") %>

  <main class="hs-section hs-section-muted">
    <div class="hs-container" style="max-width: 800px;">

      <header class="hs-section-header" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>
          At <%= businessName %>, we respect your privacy and are committed to handling
          your information in a secure and transparent way.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="hs-content">

        <h2>Who Handles Your Information</h2>
        <p>
          Hiatt Services uses <strong>Jobber</strong> to manage all customer information,
          work requests, and project details. Any information you submit through our
          website is securely collected and stored by Jobber on our behalf.
        </p>
        <p>
          Hiatt Services does not host or maintain separate copies of your data on our own servers.
        </p>

        <h2>What Information Is Collected</h2>
        <p>
          When you request a quote or contact us about a project, you may provide details such as:
        </p>
        <ul class="hs-list">
          <li>Your name</li>
          <li>Your phone number and/or email address</li>
          <li>Your property address or service location</li>
          <li>Basic information about your project or service needs</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          This information is used only so we can understand your project and respond to your request.
        </p>

        <h2>How Your Information Is Used</h2>
        <p>
          User-submitted data is stored in Jobber’s system and is used exclusively so Hiatt Services can:
        </p>
        <ul class="hs-list">
          <li>Contact you regarding your project or service request</li>
          <li>Provide quotes and schedule site visits or services</li>
          <li>Follow up about work completed or ongoing projects</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do <strong>not</strong> use your information for unrelated marketing without your consent,
          and we do <strong>not</strong> share it with unrelated third parties.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Commitment to Your Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Hiatt Services will never store, sell, or collect customer data outside of Jobber.</strong>
          All user-submitted data is held and secured by Jobber, where it is used solely to allow
          Hiatt Services to contact you regarding your project and manage our work with you.
        </p>

        <h2>Jobber’s Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
          Because Jobber is responsible for securing and managing your data, we encourage you
          to review their privacy policy for more detailed information on how your information
          is protected:
        </p>
        <p>
          <a
            href="https://www.getjobber.com/privacy-policy/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="hs-link"
          >
            View Jobber’s Privacy Policy
          </a>
        </p>

        <h2>Questions About This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how your information is handled,
          please contact us:
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Phone:</strong>
          <a href="tel:<%= phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '') %>"><%= phone %></a><br />
        </p>

      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>
